OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,FA dad-of-two who was infected with
OL,8,Fhepatitis C after receiving
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood as a child has said
OL,10,Fthe UK Government's compensation
OL,11,Fscheme "isn't good enough" as many
OL,12,Fwill not live to see the payments.
OL,14,FThe government confirmed on Tuesday
OL,15,Fthat everyone "infected or affected"
OL,16,Fby the scandal will receive
OL,17,Fcompensation, some before the end of
OL,18,Fthe year, with interim payments of
OL,19,F#210,000 for the most urgent cases to
OL,20,Fbe made from the summer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/18
