OL,7,FPaymaster General John Glen said he
OL,8,Frecognises "time is of the essence",
OL,9,Fwith members of the infected blood
OL,10,Fcommunity dying every week.
OL,12,FIt comes after the Infected Blood
OL,13,FInquiry concluded that the biggest
OL,14,Ftreatment disaster in the NHS "could
OL,15,Flargely have been avoided" and there
OL,16,Fwas a "pervasive" cover-up to hide the
OL,17,Ftruth.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/18
