OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,FDavid Thomas, from Llanharry, Rhondda
OL,8,FCynon Taf, received contaminated blood
OL,9,Fwhen he was around 10 years old during
OL,10,Fwhile receiving treatment for
OL,11,Fhaemophilia in the early 1980s.
OL,13,FBut he was not told he had hepatitis C
OL,14,Funtil he was 24, and even then was not
OL,15,Faware he had been part of such a big
OL,16,Fscandal.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/18
