OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,FHe did not tell anyone outside of his
OL,8,Fimmediate family out of fear of the
OL,9,Fstigma attached to the virus, and only
OL,10,Fbegan speaking publicly about it after
OL,11,Fa biopsy in 2010 showed he had
OL,12,Fdeveloped liver disease as a result of
OL,13,Fthe hepatitis.
OL,15,FNow 52, he was cleared of the virus in
OL,16,F2016 after a fight for access to
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/18
