OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales from his
OL,8,Fhome with his wife Kate, David said he
OL,9,Ffelt a mixture of happiness and
OL,10,Fsadness about the conclusion of the
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,F"Happiness that the report has come up
OL,14,Fwith the findings that it has," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"It's vindicating everything the
OL,18,Fcampaign has been trying to get
OL,19,Fthrough to successive governments for
OL,20,F40 years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/18
