OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"Sadness that it has taken this long
OL,8,Fand that so many people have died."
OL,10,FDavid, who has struggled with
OL,11,Fdepression as a result of his ordeal,
OL,12,Fsaid he couldn't access things like
OL,13,Flife insurance, travel insurance or
OL,14,Fmortgage protection because of his
OL,15,Fcondition. He received an interim
OL,16,Fcompensation payment of #100,000 last
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/18
