OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,FOn Tuesday's compensation
OL,8,Fannouncement, David said: "It's as far-
OL,9,Freaching as I thought it would go. I
OL,10,Fwas a bit concerned about appeals and
OL,11,Fpeople's eligibility but they seem to
OL,12,Fcovered that off.
OL,14,F"So on the whole with the compensation
OL,15,Fscheme, the initial sight looks OK.
OL,17,F"There will be another interim payment
OL,18,Fmade. What the overall package looks
OL,19,Flike, I have no idea.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
