OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"Undoubtedly there will be more
OL,8,Fquestions that arise from this. At the
OL,9,Fmoment it's still not clear in terms
OL,10,Fof a timeline or quantity of money.
OL,12,F"It's still not clear how it will be
OL,13,Fassessed and if it will be someone
OL,14,Fmaking a judgement on how they think
OL,15,Fyou've been impacted."
OL,17,FDavid said he is worried for those
OL,18,Fimpacted who may not live to see
OL,19,Fcompensation being paid.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/18
