OL,7,FHe also questioned whether those
OL,8,Faffected by the scandal who have since
OL,9,Fdied will receive compensation to
OL,10,Ftheir estate, like his mother, Jean,
OL,11,Fwho died at the start of this year.
OL,13,FHis cousin, Leigh Sugar, also a
OL,14,Fhaemophiliac, died after contracting
OL,15,Fhepatitis C at around the same time.
OL,17,F"As a community of people we've lived
OL,18,Fwith this can being kicked down the
OL,19,Froad time and time again," he said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/18
