OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"It does concern me, people like my
OL,8,Fmother, who had to live with the
OL,9,Fstress of her son having contracted
OL,10,Fthis for 30-odd years and having to
OL,11,Flive with the guilt.
OL,13,F"She's not here to fight for that
OL,14,Fmoney that she was due so it might get
OL,15,Fcast aside.
OL,17,F"By April 2025, when this scheme will
OL,18,Fallegedly take place, another 70 to
OL,19,F100 people will have died.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/18
