OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"It isn't good enough. The payments
OL,8,Fshould be made now. The report has
OL,9,Fbeen published. The government have
OL,10,Frun the numbers and they know roughly
OL,11,Fwhat it'll cost.
OL,13,F"It's beyond me why those payments
OL,14,Fcouldn't be made to the people
OL,15,Finfected, certainly. It's not good
OL,16,Fenough."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/18
