OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"It seems to be clear that those who
OL,8,Fare already registered on a financial
OL,9,Fsupport scheme will be automatically
OL,10,Feligible for this new financial
OL,11,Fcompensation scheme.
OL,13,F"However there are clients who weren't
OL,14,Feligible for those, for example people
OL,15,Finfected after September 1, 1991, but
OL,16,Falso crucially, people who haven't
OL,17,Fbeen able to prove that they had a
OL,18,Fblood transfusion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/18
