OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"Often it's people who had hepatitis C
OL,8,Fwho had a transfusion in the seventies
OL,9,For eighties who weren't diagnosed for
OL,10,Fabout 30 years and when they went back
OL,11,Fto get their records they had been
OL,12,Fdestroyed, so those people have never
OL,13,Fbeen eligible for any kind of
OL,14,Ffinancial support."
OL,16,FBut Ms Morgan said the compensation
OL,17,Fannouncement was "significant".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/18
