OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"People have campaigned for decades
OL,8,Fjust to have some kind of recognition
OL,9,Fof the fact that this has happened to
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"Closure and redress comes in lots of
OL,13,Fdifferent formats and will be
OL,14,Fdifferent for everybody but at least a
OL,15,Fcommitment to a full and proper
OL,16,Fcompensation scheme does go some way
OL,17,Fin addressing concerns.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/18
