OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"It's unfortunate that it's taken so
OL,8,Flong to get to this point. Whilst we
OL,9,Fare pleased that this announcement has
OL,10,Fcome today, we and our clients would
OL,11,Fhave hoped it would have come a lot
OL,12,Fsooner than this.
OL,14,F"The extent of the failures found
OL,15,Fagainst individuals will need to be
OL,16,Fexamined closely and whether there's a
OL,17,Fcall for stripping people of their
OL,18,Ftitles, we'll need to consider that
OL,19,Fclosely with our clients and there may
OL,20,Fwell be a campaign for that in the
OL,21,Ffuture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/18
