OL,3,CInfected blood victim says
OL,4,Ccompensation 'isn't good enough' as
OL,5,Cwait goes on
OL,7,F"In terms of bringing criminal
OL,8,Fproceedings against individuals, it
OL,9,Fmay just be too late for that to have
OL,10,Fany effect, possibly because they're
OL,11,Fno longer with us or the public
OL,12,Finterest, because they are so elderly.
OL,14,F"Although compensation is a huge part
OL,15,Fof this, there are lots of other
OL,16,Frecommendations that are very
OL,17,Fsignificant for our clients, both in
OL,18,Fterms of additional support that they
OL,19,Fand their families need, but also
OL,20,Fmaking sure this never happens again.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/18
